<h2 id="client-credentials-flow">Client Credentials Flow</h2>
<blockquote>
  <p><strong>REF</strong> <a href="https://developer.spotify.com/documentation/general/guides/authorization-guide/" target="_blank">Authorization Guide</a> : OAuthê°€ ì•„ë‹ˆë¯€ë¡œ Web API ë¶€ë¶„ ì°¸ê³ </p>
